  <summary date="2023-03-06T16:35:35Z" status="Public Law">Iran Hostages Congressional Gold Medal Act

This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to the 53 hostages of the Iran Hostage Crisis (November 4, 1979-January 21, 1981) in recognition of their bravery and endurance throughout their captivity.</summary>
